{"tid":2044071,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"婉衡開班教健身Chur爆　兩位數試玩價男學生爭住上","createTime":"2020-05-31T00:37:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T20:59:18.000Z","uid":137088,"like":8,"dislike":189,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"4c15583a0a76c6ed2c73111323c659996453f244","tid":2044071,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T00:37:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200530/343398020185985024.jpeg/PYju7bznOfK0mTO4j1hLptijYxHm6QRX6UnFcOlJxXA?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200530%2F343398020185985024.jpeg%2FPYju7bznOfK0mTO4j1hLptijYxHm6QRX6UnFcOlJxXA%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=c1ddf74e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200529/343153713592012800.jpeg/Wlj37jBNqPG4p2UtLQJTJh0ngPpzWuz3rj6oeK4-qHg?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200529%2F343153713592012800.jpeg%2FWlj37jBNqPG4p2UtLQJTJh0ngPpzWuz3rj6oeK4-qHg%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=1c3e141e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200529/343152144574189568.jpeg/WDNGwBhkRFe4AAfuOzpl3L4ZyvVP56rd0BDWj9AQ1o8?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200529%2F343152144574189568.jpeg%2FWDNGwBhkRFe4AAfuOzpl3L4ZyvVP56rd0BDWj9AQ1o8%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=0a589f56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200529/343153223676334080.jpeg/DluryQfjWqBF7LEg3DHIxrDTLPUDkw7r0qb2jdKm9o0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200529%2F343153223676334080.jpeg%2FDluryQfjWqBF7LEg3DHIxrDTLPUDkw7r0qb2jdKm9o0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=002dd6dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200529/343153711369031681.jpeg/37IpTDX2NlUuZ7M_KnzkcyVn5R2ol864abjv5mm47-Y?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200529%2F343153711369031681.jpeg%2F37IpTDX2NlUuZ7M_KnzkcyVn5R2ol864abjv5mm47-Y%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=8a35c4e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200529/343153715559141376.jpeg/4arrMKuqn1pJarH-2iC8VCppctqJS_Zx3jtNWd47TVk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200529%2F343153715559141376.jpeg%2F4arrMKuqn1pJarH-2iC8VCppctqJS_Zx3jtNWd47TVk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=71865689&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《3日2夜》女神陳婉衡（Alycia）出名身材火辣，熱愛健身的她自從以過萬元考獲健身教練牌，於上月就開始在陳庭欣男友楊振源（Benny）投資的健身室「掛牌」做星級導師，女神一星期開一堂教大家做核心肌肉訓練！<br />\n<br />\n自從上月Alycia開班消息一傳出，隨即惹來大批男學生搶住上堂，加上健身室大酬賓，試玩價只需88元，真是相當抵玩，難怪每堂廿個名額秒速被Book爆，就連準老闆娘陳庭欣都在IG大呻：「Full到連我都冇位上堂。」<br />\n<br />\nAlycia接受《香港01》訪問時就透露：「其實我4月就開始教，教咗幾堂Gym room就閂咗門，初初都比較多男仔，我自己都有少少意想唔到，去到後尾都多番女仔，都有3、4成係女仔。」問男學生們有否專心上堂？她指：「大家都好乖好認真去上，但初初教Group Class未搵到個平衡，可能就比較Chur咗啲，好多同學仔都做得好吃力，初初唔係咁跟得上，之後我就慢慢調整番個程度係啱番所有人，爆汗得嚟又應付到。」<br />\n<br />\n問反應是否很熱烈？她笑稱：「初初教場場都爆滿。呢排Gym Room開返，但我又唔小心拉親條筋，所以呢兩個禮拜就唞一唞，希望下個禮拜可以教番。（啲男學生追你咁點算？）點算？冇呀，咪睇大家夾唔夾囉。」看來Alycia都不排除發展師生戀，看來健身班又要場場爆滿了。"},{"pid":"8c3767fa35a18800cfe04eb62f03d9ccb69a9035","tid":2044071,"uid":50595,"like":139,"dislike":0,"score":139,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T00:40:31.000Z","msg":"樣衰版julia<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66ccaba4a2e2eef24c7745d313734c2e00e1658","tid":2044071,"uid":54486,"like":424,"dislike":1,"score":423,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T00:47:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GQRiq5C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGQRiq5C.png&h=f9adcd18&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b97865e797518c8c70f310dc8c3bc9e686161e0a","tid":2044071,"uid":159313,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"a66ccaba4a2e2eef24c7745d313734c2e00e1658","tid":2044071,"uid":54486,"like